            <noteGrp type="workDesc">
               <note type="description">A short prayer of protection, widely circulated. Commonly known also as al-Dawr al-aʿlā or Dawr al-aʿlā. OY lists nine separate commentaries, which appear to have been written in 12–13th centuries.</note>
               <note type="structure">Structure of Work</note>
